@startuml approach2-abbreviated
title **Approach 2: InMemoryCosmosClient + InMemoryContainer — Query Flow (Abbreviated)**

skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam sequenceArrowThickness 2

actor "Test Code" as Test
participant "InMemoryCosmosClient" as Client
participant "InMemoryDatabase" as DB
participant "InMemoryContainer" as IMC
participant "CosmosSqlParser" as Parser
participant "InMemoryFeedIterator<T>" as FeedIter

== Setup ==
Test -> Client ** : new InMemoryCosmosClient(…)

== Get Container (lazy creation) ==

Test -> Client ++ : GetContainer(databaseId, containerId)
Client -> DB ** : GetOrAdd → InMemoryDatabase [if new]
Client -> DB : GetOrCreateContainer()
DB -> IMC ** : GetOrAdd → InMemoryContainer [if new]
Client --> Test -- : Container (InMemoryContainer)

== Query Execution (identical to Approach 1) ==

Test -> IMC ++ : GetItemQueryIterator<T>(queryText)
IMC -> Parser ++ : Parse(queryText)
Parser --> IMC -- : CosmosSqlQuery (AST)
IMC -> IMC : FilterItemsByQuery()\n→ WHERE / ORDER BY / SELECT / …
IMC -> FeedIter ** : InMemoryFeedIterator<T>
IMC --> Test -- : FeedIterator<T>

loop while HasMoreResults
  Test -> FeedIter ++ : ReadNextAsync()
  FeedIter --> Test -- : FeedResponse<T>
end

note over IMC
  LINQ flow also identical to Approach 1:
  GetItemLinqQueryable<T>() → LINQ-to-Objects
  → .ToFeedIteratorOverridable()
end note

@enduml
